A place where ideas are stored and worked on iteratively. Its purpose is to promote networked-thought by encouraging the gardener to keep connecting ideas.

It gives our minds a place where to think with the [[right balance of chaos and structure to increase creativity|Creativity benefits from chaos and structure]].